CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1953, pg. 7, reads: "Fellowship Service Leaders - Leaders at World Fellowship Service which featured Miss Dorothy Height as guest speaker are shown here. Left to right: Miss Nancy Lee, Mrs. Nancy Lee, Mrs. Ethel Ramos Harris, B.H. Logan, Miss Dorothy Height, guest speaker; Mrs. George L. West and Mrs. Florence May, who presided during the program in auditorium of Central YMCA, Chatham Street, Sunday April 29. Not in the picture, Mrs. Alma A. Polk and Mrs. Mildred Young. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Nancy Lee, Ethel Ramos Harris, B. H. Logan, Dorothy Height, Mrs. George L. West, and Florence May, gathered for World Fellowship Service program at Central YWCA, Chatham Street
